reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Make your event more custom
reviews.reviewText: We purchased these for a baby shower and they made it look that much more put together. Some of the pieces we had to toss, as the handle wasn't attached to utensil very well, but that was just a few. I still give it 5 stars for the what you get for the money. They have a ton of colors and they were sturdy to eat with.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars PERFECT for entertaining - look so classy!
reviews.reviewText: First of all - This is plasticware and performs like plasticware. It isn't any "firmer" than a regular set of disposable silverware. BUT. 5/5 would recommend because it looks absolutely amazing and shines on any table! We used for 2 different parties and I probably won't use any other type of disposable ware now because why would I when this works perfectly and makes entertaining fun and beautiful?! Do yourself a favor and buy a set - it's a large number of utensils but just keep some on hand at all times to pull out for any occasion you may have.
